  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 200.",
    "Roll out the puff pastry, place it on a baking sheet and cut into small squares.",
    "Whisk together coconut cream, smoked garlic puree, tomato paste, oregano, cayenne pepper, and vegetable stock. Mix well until smooth.",
    "Brush olive oil over each puff pastry square, then pour the mixture on top of each.",
    "Bake for 25 minutes or until golden brown.",
    "Serve warm with a side salad."
